                                    <locus from="1r" to="6r" scheme="folios"/> paginated 1-11 in dark brown ink by a modern hand, <locus from="7r" to="124r" scheme="folios"/> foliated 7-124 in pencil by a modern hand. </foliation>
                                <collation>
                                    <formula>1(6), 2-15(8), 16(6)</formula>
                                    <p>
                                        <ref target="https://vceditor.library.upenn.edu/project/6825dfdbf060c60001cc0fd9/viewOnly">VisColl collation.</ref> Two folios at the end, <locus from="121r" to="122v" scheme="folios"/>, should be placed before <locus from="119" to="119" scheme="folios"/>.</p>
