                        <additions>
                            <p>
                                <locus from="LCI" to="LCI" scheme="other"/>
                                <note>Top of page, in pencil by a modern hand: <quote>A:28</quote> (current signum). In brown ink by a modern hand: <quote>21 B</quote>. In brown ink by a medieval hand: <quote>prima secunde</quote>. In brown ink by two early modern hands: <quote>Martyrologia Sive descriptio Brevis omnium Martyrum Singulis Anni Diebus adscriptum Ecclesiae olim Stregnensis</quote>. National Library book label with current signum in black ink. Bottom of page, in brown ink by an early modern hand: <quote>N:9</quote> (unidentified signum).</note>
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <locus from="RCI" to="RCI" scheme="other"/>
                                <note>Musical notation, of unknown date, in black ink.</note>
                            </p>
                        </additions>
                        <bindingDesc>
                            <binding contemporary="true">
                                <p>Medieval binding. Dark brown skin over wooden boards. 4 double raised bands and 2 endbands. On <locus from="Spine" to="Spine" scheme="other"/>, stamped in gold: the current signum <quote>A 28</quote>. Remnants of a clasp on <locus from="LCO" to="LCO" scheme="other"/>, marks of a clasp on <locus from="RCO" to="RCO" scheme="other"/>. The straps are missing.</p>
                                <p>
                                    <dimensions type="binding">
                                        <height unit="mm" max="60" min="60"/>
                                        <width unit="mm" max="190" min="190"/>
                                        <depth unit="mm" max="270" min="270"/>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </p>
                                <condition>The volume has been repaired; the spine is modern.</condition>
                            </binding>
                        </bindingDesc>
